   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&#x2018;Institutions for Inclusive Development&#x2019; (I4ID) (implementation phase)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">I4ID is a 5 year programme which aims to strengthen democratic institutions and governance in Tanzania so that they are more inclusive and accountable, and economic growth provides more benefits for poor people. DFID has stipulated that I4ID be delivered using an &#x201C;adaptive management&#x201D; approach, which emphasises flexibility and a continual process of testing, monitoring, seeking feedback and correcting course if necessary within the lifespan of the project.</narrative>
